import React from 'react'
import './footer.css'

import { Container, Row, Col, ListGroup, ListGroupItem } from 'reactstrap';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <footer className='footer'>
      <Container>
        <Row>
          <Col lg></Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
    </footer>
    </>
  )
}

export default Footer
